snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 x Exoprimal - DLC Reveal Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2023
snippet.description: If you always wanted to see Ryu fight a dinosaur, this Street Fighter x Exoprimal collab will let you live that dream on July 14, 2023 in Street Fighter 6.
